tva:BasicDescription.tva:Title: Is Honduras Safe To Travel To?
tva:BasicDescription.tva:Synopsis: More than 350 volunteers from all over the world worked together to build schools in northern Honduras this January. We interviewed the volunteers at the worksites to ask how safe they felt during the trip, and if the media stories on Honduras felt accurate.
